                    "body": "Can you share your virtualhost and host file entries please? I'm trying to reproduce.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=merrix",
                        "name": "merrix",
                        "displayName": "Grayson Koonce",
